<div class="list-pages-box">    

<p>WhiteGuard has been a member of this site since the 17th of December, 2014, and as of the time of writing, he has contributed a total of 1 SCP Article, 0 Tales, 0 GoI Formats, and 12 other pages on the site. WhiteGuard's most popular page on the site by rating is <a href="/meet-the-administrators-zyn">Meet the Administrators - Zyn</a> at +63. He became a member of Junior Staff on the 9th of May, 2020 by joining the <a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/community-outreach-main">Community Outreach Team</a> and later the <a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/maintenance-and-ancillary-staff-team-main">Maintenance and Ancillary Staff Team</a> and the <a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/license-experts-main">Licensing Team</a>. On the 10th of October, 2020, he was promoted to Operational Staff. In addition to his staff work, he happens to be our non-official site interviewer with his 2 excellent series of interviews called <a href="/meet-the-administrators-hub">Meet the Administrators</a> and <a href="/interviewing-icons-hub">Interviewing Icons</a>. His 9 total written interviews make him the holder for the most total written interviews on the site with the user <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610202865" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">RJB_R</a></span> in second with 1. The following interview will consist of 11 questions from myself and 4 questions from the community with his responses.</p>

    
    
    
